00:13:12.660 --> 00:13:15.170 position:56%
to tinker with it as you're writing.

00:13:15.170 --> 00:13:19.250
&gt;&gt; Don Winslow: Yeah, I was as a
kid very influenced by those sort

00:13:19.250 --> 00:13:24.780
