00:40:26.070 --> 00:40:29.950 position:56%
It's easily my favorite of the year.

00:40:29.950 --> 00:40:31.250
&gt;&gt; Don Winslow: Thank you.

00:40:31.250 --> 00:40:34.240
&gt;&gt; It's a very New York book
