00:41:32.390 --> 00:41:33.690
&gt;&gt; Don Winslow: Yeah, me too.

00:41:33.690 --> 00:41:34.990
&gt;&gt; Sounds like [inaudible] --

00:41:34.990 --> 00:41:36.910
