00:41:38.590 --> 00:41:41.390
So I'm curious how one
goes from getting a degree

00:41:41.390 --> 00:41:43.510
in African Studies to being a P.I.

00:41:43.510 --> 00:41:45.010
in Time Square no less?

00:41:45.010 --> 00:41:47.100 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Don Winslow: The long way, ma'am.

00:41:47.100 --> 00:41:51.080
Look, I don't want to
be ironic about it.

00:41:51.080 --> 00:41:53.890
I just needed to make money.

00:41:53.890 --> 00:41:59.170
I had to pay rent and --
and so I tried to do things

00:41:59.170 --> 00:42:01.640
that were interesting
and a little different,

00:42:01.640 --> 00:42:04.660
