00:42:36.420 --> 00:42:39.660
that kind of thing and instead I
could go and be absolutely broke

00:42:39.660 --> 00:42:42.850
and be a safari bum and
live from moment to moment.

00:42:42.850 --> 00:42:44.540
So of course I made that choice.

00:42:44.540 --> 00:42:46.500
Thank you.

00:42:46.500 --> 00:42:48.340
Yes, Dodgers fan.

00:42:48.340 --> 00:42:49.640
&gt;&gt; Hi.

00:42:49.640 --> 00:42:50.940
