points of view.

00:43:07.060 --> 00:43:08.490
This is all from Malone.

00:43:08.490 --> 00:43:09.790
&gt;&gt; Don Winslow: Yeah, thank you.

00:43:09.790 --> 00:43:11.090
That's, again, a very
astute question.

00:43:11.090 --> 00:43:13.120
It's the only book
I've done that with.

00:43:13.120 --> 00:43:15.430
There's a technical phrase
for it that I'm not aware of.

00:43:15.430 --> 00:43:18.890
So I'm going to mention it in the
