00:44:05.620 --> 00:44:09.860
And so I made that
decision albeit reluctantly

00:44:09.860 --> 00:44:11.520
to stay just with Malone.

00:44:11.520 --> 00:44:14.180
I've never done it before, and I
don't know if I'll do it again.

